Package: diagrambot
Title: Voice Assistant for Mermaid and Graphviz Diagrams
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Interactive Shiny app that generates Mermaid and Graphviz diagrams from voice commands using GPT-4o Realtime. Supports flowcharts, sequence diagrams, network graphs, organizational charts, and more.
